## üìä Test Artifacts

### E2E Test Suite
- **Location:** `/tests/e2e/vibelife-frontend.spec.ts`
- **Test Count:** 20 tests across 6 categories
- **Duration:** 13.5 seconds
- **Framework:** Playwright + Chromium

### Screenshots
- **Location:** `/tests/e2e/screenshots/`
- **Count:** 13 screenshots
- **Coverage:**
  - Homepage (desktop, tablet, mobile)
  - Bazi chat interface (desktop, mobile)
  - Zodiac chat interface (desktop)
  - Various interaction states

### Commands
```bash
# Run all tests
npx playwright test

# View HTML report
npx playwright show-report

# Run specific test
npx playwright test tests/e2e/vibelife-frontend.spec.ts

# Run in UI mode (interactive)
npx playwright test --ui
```

